      <title>拜登在新一轮救济中取消了 60 亿美元的学生债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/student-loan-forgiveness-biden-cancels-6-billion-in-latest-round</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统为近 78,000 名从事公共服务的美国人免除了近 60 亿美元的联邦学生债务，这是他在 11 月大选前实施其标志性举措之一的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/student-loan-forgiveness-biden-cancels-6-billion-in-latest-round</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
