    <item>
      <title>自杀式炸弹袭击者袭击阿富汗银行，造成三人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-21/a-suicide-bomber-attacks-a-bank-in-afghanistan-killing-at-least-3-people-and-injuring-12-others</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊斯兰堡（美联社）——官员称，周四，一名自杀式炸弹袭击者袭击了阿富汗南部坎大哈市的一家私人银行，造成至少 3 人死亡、12 人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-21/a-suicide-bomber-attacks-a-bank-in-afghanistan-killing-at-least-3-people-and-injuring-12-others</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 07:35:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚称已结清 70 亿美元外汇积压的有效索赔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/nigeria-says-cleared-valid-claims-of-7-billion-forex-backlog</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚央行已解决所有有效的外汇积压问题，旨在稳定市场并恢复投资者对经济的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/nigeria-says-cleared-valid-claims-of-7-billion-forex-backlog</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 07:13:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国会公布 9 月 30 日之前向各机构提供 1.2 万亿美元资金的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/congress-unveils-1-2-trillion-plan-to-fund-agencies-to-sept-30</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会领导人公布了一项价值 1.2 万亿美元的协议的细节，该协议旨在让大多数美国政府机构在 9 月 30 日之前保持开放，而就在周六部分政府关门的最后期限前几天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/congress-unveils-1-2-trillion-plan-to-fund-agencies-to-sept-30</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 07:04:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>邮报称，泰国国王分居的儿子考虑回国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/thai-king-s-estranged-son-mulls-returning-to-country-post-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《曼谷邮报》报道，泰国国王玛哈·哇集拉隆功的儿子已获得政府颁发的身份证和泰国护照，在国外生活了近三十年后，现在打算返回这个东南亚国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/thai-king-s-estranged-son-mulls-returning-to-country-post-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 05:57:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰击落俄罗斯对基辅的所有导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/eight-injured-in-new-russian-missile-attack-on-kyiv-mayor-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰空军击落了俄罗斯自2月份以来对基辅的首次大规模袭击中发射的全部31枚导弹，这表明尽管延迟接受军事援助，首都的防空能力仍然强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/eight-injured-in-new-russian-missile-attack-on-kyiv-mayor-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 04:01:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙中右翼领导人在选举中以微弱优势获胜后被任命为总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/portugal-s-center-right-leader-named-prime-minister-after-narrow-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙中右翼领导人路易斯·黑山在其联盟本月以微弱优势赢得选举后被任命为总理，这给他带来了试图以少数派政府执政的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/portugal-s-center-right-leader-named-prime-minister-after-narrow-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 00:26:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>跨越俄罗斯边境的袭击让人们认识到普京战争的代价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/attacks-near-russia-s-ukraine-border-bring-home-costs-of-putin-s-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对与乌克兰接壤的俄罗斯地区的致命袭击越来越让人认识到弗拉基米尔·普京入侵的代价。这并不意味着人们会因战争而攻击俄罗斯总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/attacks-near-russia-s-ukraine-border-bring-home-costs-of-putin-s-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 16:00:52 GMT</pubDate>
